entries.femaleVariant: Looking for a new implant.
Saw a different ripper here before.
Been thinkin’ about gettin' some new chrome.
Then I think you’ve come to the right place.
You new here? Seem to remember this ugly, slimy gonk – type with oozing flesh, running this shop.
entries.maleVariant: You new here? Seem to remember this ugly, slimy gonk – type with oozing flesh, runnin' this shop.

entries.femaleVariant: My uncle is not a handsome man, I know, but he is hard to forget once you see him.
Preem, yeah... Nothin’ like serving up a howler first time you meet someone, talk to ‘em.
You think it a mistake to speak the truth?
True or not, it was rude, hurtful – what else would you call it if not a mistake?
And that is why I love to travel. Words – we think we know how to use them, but then there is context...
Just started out in this biz?
So, just startin’ out in this biz?
No, I move around in this biz. I’ve run shops in Irkutsk , Leningrad, Vienna and Glasgow. I thought it was time to try Night City.
My uncle rented me the shop because it was my birthday. I’m thirty. I will sit here and run the business until I get bored.
Night City - whaddaya think of it?
So, our city of dreams – whaddaya make of it?
It’s wonderful! Compared to the USSR, so different.
Like it that much, really?
Yes, terribly! You shoot at each other in the street, you must pay for first aid, emergency help...
It’s a nightmare... but sooo interesting!
